---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout locale="en" title="For Businesses — ClosersMatch" description="Outsource your sales to certified closers and appointment setters. No cure no pay. No fixed salary, no recruitment fees. Pay only for results.">

  <!-- ================================================
       HERO
  ================================================ -->
  <section class="vb-hero">
    <div class="container vb-hero__inner">
      <div class="vb-hero__content">
        <span class="label label--red">For businesses</span>
        <h1 class="vb-hero__title">
          Stop losing leads.<br />
          <span class="vb-hero__title-red">Pay only for deals.</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="vb-hero__subtitle">
          ClosersMatch connects you with certified closers and appointment setters who take over your sales process. No fixed salary. No recruitment fees. No risk. Only results.
        </p>
        <div class="vb-hero__trust-pills">
          <span class="trust-pill">✓ No cure no pay</span>
          <span class="trust-pill">✓ Match within 48 hours</span>
          <span class="trust-pill">✓ Free onboarding</span>
        </div>
        <div class="vb-hero__actions">
          <a href="/en/contact" class="btn btn--red btn--lg">Book your free intake →</a>
          <a href="#hoe-het-werkt" class="btn btn--outline-dark-mode">How it works</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="vb-hero__visual">
        <div class="vb-hero__stats-card">
          <div class="vb-stat">
            <span class="vb-stat__num">€50K</span>
            <span class="vb-stat__label">Deal closed in week 1</span>
            <span class="vb-stat__company">DetachPro</span>
          </div>
          <div class="vb-stat-divider"></div>
          <div class="vb-stat">
            <span class="vb-stat__num">€20K+</span>
            <span class="vb-stat__label">Per month in new deals</span>
            <span class="vb-stat__company">Leadstars</span>
          </div>
          <div class="vb-stat-divider"></div>
          <div class="vb-stat">
            <span class="vb-stat__num">48u</span>
            <span class="vb-stat__label">Average time to first match</span>
            <span class="vb-stat__company">ClosersMatch guarantee</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ================================================
       PIJNPUNTEN
  ================================================ -->
  <section class="section vb-pijn">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="vb-pijn__header">
        <span class="label">Sound familiar?</span>
        <h2 class="h2 vb-pijn__title">Your company does not lack<br />leads.<br /><span class="vb-pijn__title-red">It lacks revenue.</span></h2>
        <p class="vb-pijn__sub">Most companies have enough opportunities. The challenge is turning them into customers consistently. Here is where your revenue leaks out:</p>
      </div>

      <div class="vb-pijn__grid">
        <div class="vb-pijn__item">
          <div class="vb-pijn__icon">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12" y2="12"/><line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12.01" y2="16"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="vb-pijn__item-title">Leads without follow-up</h3>
            <p class="vb-pijn__item-text">Warm leads that never get called. No systematic follow-up. Opportunities that simply walk away.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="vb-pijn__item">
          <div class="vb-pijn__icon">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 00-4-4H5a4 4 0 00-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 00-3-3.87M16 3.13a4 4 0 010 7.75"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="vb-pijn__item-title">Sales capacity blocking growth</h3>
            <p class="vb-pijn__item-text">Growth depends on one or two people. Scaling is impossible without risk or high costs.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="vb-pijn__item">
          <div class="vb-pijn__icon">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="12" y1="1" x2="12" y2="23"/><path d="M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 000 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 010 7H6"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="vb-pijn__item-title">Hiring is expensive and risky</h3>
            <p class="vb-pijn__item-text">Months of searching, onboarding, training, and still disappointed. Fixed salary, no guarantee of results.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="vb-pijn__item">
          <div class="vb-pijn__icon">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="22 12 18 12 15 21 9 3 6 12 2 12"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="vb-pijn__item-title">No insight into commercial performance</h3>
            <p class="vb-pijn__item-text">What gets called? How many appointments? Which deals are in progress? Without data, there is no control.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="vb-pijn__item">
          <div class="vb-pijn__icon">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M10.29 3.86L1.82 18a2 2 0 001.71 3h16.94a2 2 0 001.71-3L13.71 3.86a2 2 0 00-3.42 0z"/><line x1="12" y1="9" x2="12" y2="13"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12.01" y2="17"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="vb-pijn__item-title">Previous closers who underperformed</h3>
            <p class="vb-pijn__item-text">Disappointing experiences with freelancers or hires who did not close as expected.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="vb-pijn__item">
          <div class="vb-pijn__icon">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2"/><path d="M3 9h18M9 21V9"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="vb-pijn__item-title">Growth that depends on too few people</h3>
            <p class="vb-pijn__item-text">One person gets sick, leaves, or underperforms, and your entire sales process grinds to a halt.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ================================================
       WAAROM CLOSERSMATCH
  ================================================ -->
  <section class="section vb-waarom">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="vb-waarom__header">
        <span class="label">Why ClosersMatch</span>
        <h2 class="h2 vb-waarom__title">Traditional hiring brings risk.<br />ClosersMatch works on results.</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="vb-waarom__compare">

        <!-- Traditioneel -->
        <div class="vb-compare-col vb-compare-col--old">
          <div class="vb-compare-col__header">
            <span class="vb-compare-col__tag vb-compare-col__tag--gray">Traditional hiring</span>
          </div>
          <ul class="vb-compare-list">
            <li class="vb-compare-item vb-compare-item--no">
              <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round"><line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"/><line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"/></svg>
              Post a job and review résumés
            </li>
            <li class="vb-compare-item vb-compare-item--no">
              <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round"><line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"/><line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"/></svg>
              Wait weeks to months
            </li>
            <li class="vb-compare-item vb-compare-item--no">
              <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round"><line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"/><line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"/></svg>
              Fixed salary regardless of performance
            </li>
            <li class="vb-compare-item vb-compare-item--no">
              <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round"><line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"/><line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"/></svg>
              Expensive onboarding and training
            </li>
            <li class="vb-compare-item vb-compare-item--no">
              <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round"><line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"/><line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"/></svg>
              No guarantee of results
            </li>
            <li class="vb-compare-item vb-compare-item--no">
              <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round"><line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"/><line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"/></svg>
              Employer risk and contracts
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- vs -->
        <div class="vb-compare-vs">VS</div>

        <!-- ClosersMatch -->
        <div class="vb-compare-col vb-compare-col--new">
          <div class="vb-compare-col__header">
            <span class="vb-compare-col__tag vb-compare-col__tag--red">ClosersMatch</span>
          </div>
          <ul class="vb-compare-list">
            <li class="vb-compare-item vb-compare-item--yes">
              <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              Free onboarding included
            </li>
            <li class="vb-compare-item vb-compare-item--yes">
              <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              Match within 48 hours
            </li>
            <li class="vb-compare-item vb-compare-item--yes">
              <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              No cure no pay, pay only for results
            </li>
            <li class="vb-compare-item vb-compare-item--yes">
              <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              CM Certified closers, ready to deploy
            </li>
            <li class="vb-compare-item vb-compare-item--yes">
              <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              Full visibility via CRM and reporting
            </li>
            <li class="vb-compare-item vb-compare-item--yes">
              <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              Scalable without headcount risk
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ================================================
       HOE HET WERKT
  ================================================ -->
  <section class="section vb-hiw" id="hoe-het-werkt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="vb-hiw__header">
        <span class="label">How it works</span>
        <h2 class="h2 vb-hiw__title">From intake to closed deal.<br />In four steps.</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="vb-hiw__grid">

        <div class="vb-hiw__step">
          <div class="vb-hiw__step-num">01</div>
          <h3 class="vb-hiw__step-title">Intake</h3>
          <p class="vb-hiw__step-text">We learn your business, product, and target audience. Together we determine which profile, closer, setter, or combination, fits your sales process and deal size best.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="vb-hiw__step">
          <div class="vb-hiw__step-num">02</div>
          <h3 class="vb-hiw__step-title">Matching</h3>
          <p class="vb-hiw__step-text">Within 48 hours we connect you with CM Certified professionals. No stacks of résumés. No job interviews. We filter by industry, sales style, and track record.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="vb-hiw__step">
          <div class="vb-hiw__step-num">03</div>
          <h3 class="vb-hiw__step-title">Onboarding</h3>
          <p class="vb-hiw__step-text">The closer is onboarded on your product, market, and customer. Scripts are prepared, CRM is set up, and the process is ready. Free. That is part of the ecosystem.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="vb-hiw__step">
          <div class="vb-hiw__step-num">04</div>
          <h3 class="vb-hiw__step-title">Results</h3>
          <p class="vb-hiw__step-text">The system goes live. Leads are qualified, conversations happen, deals get closed. You see everything via the dashboard. And pay only when there are results.</p>
        </div>

      </div>

      <div class="vb-hiw__cta">
        <a href="/en/contact" class="btn btn--red btn--lg">Book your free intake →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ================================================
       RESULTATEN
  ================================================ -->
  <section class="section vb-results">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="vb-results__header">
        <span class="label label--red">Proven results</span>
        <h2 class="h2 vb-results__title">What companies achieve<br />with ClosersMatch.</h2>
        <p class="vb-results__sub">Three industries. Three matches. All with results from week one.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="vb-results__grid">

        <div class="vb-result-card">
          <div class="vb-result-card__logo-wrap">
            <img src="/images/clients/detachpro.png" alt="DetachPro" class="vb-result-card__logo" />
          </div>
          <p class="vb-result-card__desc">Connects technical professionals with companies.</p>
          <div class="vb-result-card__highlight">
            <span class="vb-result-card__arrow">→</span>
            <span>€50,000 deal closed in week one</span>
          </div>
          <p class="vb-result-card__note">No ramp-up period. Immediate commercial results.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="vb-result-card vb-result-card--featured">
          <div class="vb-result-card__logo-wrap vb-result-card__logo-wrap--dark">
            <img src="/images/clients/van-de-bilt-energy.png" alt="Van de Bilt Energy" class="vb-result-card__logo" />
          </div>
          <p class="vb-result-card__desc">Supplier of home battery systems and sustainable energy solutions.</p>
          <div class="vb-result-card__highlight">
            <span class="vb-result-card__arrow">→</span>
            <span>Two systems sold in week one</span>
          </div>
          <p class="vb-result-card__note">From lead to closed deal. Fast conversion, proven proposition.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="vb-result-card">
          <div class="vb-result-card__logo-wrap vb-result-card__logo-wrap--dark">
            <img src="/images/clients/leadstars.png" alt="Leadstars" class="vb-result-card__logo" />
          </div>
          <p class="vb-result-card__desc">Helps companies grow structurally through visibility, leads, and deals.</p>
          <div class="vb-result-card__highlight">
            <span class="vb-result-card__arrow">→</span>
            <span>€20,000+ per month in new deals</span>
          </div>
          <p class="vb-result-card__note">Consistent deal flow. Scalable and measurable.</p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ================================================
       VOOR WIE
  ================================================ -->
  <section class="section vb-voor-wie">
    <div class="container vb-voor-wie__inner">
      <div class="vb-voor-wie__content">
        <span class="label">Who is this for?</span>
        <h2 class="h2 vb-voor-wie__title">ClosersMatch works for any company that takes revenue seriously.</h2>
        <p class="vb-voor-wie__body">Whether you run a coaching business, a B2B service, a SaaS product, or a high-ticket offer, if you have warm leads that are not being closed consistently, ClosersMatch is the solution.</p>

        <div class="vb-voor-wie__usecases">
          <div class="vb-voor-wie__usecase">
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            Outsource sales without hiring staff
          </div>
          <div class="vb-voor-wie__usecase">
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            Improve lead follow-up and generate more appointments
          </div>
          <div class="vb-voor-wie__usecase">
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            Scale sales capacity quickly without risk
          </div>
          <div class="vb-voor-wie__usecase">
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            A fully outsourced sales process from A to Z
          </div>
          <div class="vb-voor-wie__usecase">
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            Drive commercial growth with insight and control
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="vb-voor-wie__card">
        <p class="vb-voor-wie__card-quote">"We had 40+ warm leads sitting unclosed. ClosersMatch provided a certified closer within a week who took our conversion rate from 18% to 61%."</p>
        <div class="vb-voor-wie__card-author">
          <div class="vb-voor-wie__avatar">JV</div>
          <div>
            <strong>Jeroen V.</strong>
            <span>CEO, Online Coaching Company</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="vb-voor-wie__card-stats">
          <div class="vb-voor-wie__card-stat">
            <span class="vb-voor-wie__stat-num">18%→61%</span>
            <span class="vb-voor-wie__stat-label">Conversion uplift</span>
          </div>
          <div class="vb-voor-wie__card-stat">
            <span class="vb-voor-wie__stat-num">1 week</span>
            <span class="vb-voor-wie__stat-label">To first deal</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ================================================
       AFSLUITENDE CTA
  ================================================ -->
  <section class="vb-closing">
    <div class="vb-closing__inner">
      <span class="label label--ghost-light">No cure no pay</span>
      <h2 class="vb-closing__title">
        Ready to stop<br />losing leads?
      </h2>
      <p class="vb-closing__body">
        Every missed lead is lost revenue. Every day without a system is a day your competitor gets closer to your customer.<br /><br />
        ClosersMatch builds your commercial ecosystem, on no cure no pay.
      </p>
      <a href="/en/contact" class="btn btn--red btn--xl vb-closing__btn">Book your free intake →</a>
      <p class="vb-closing__sub">No obligations. No upfront costs. Just a clear picture of what is possible for your business.</p>
      <p class="vb-closing__brand">ClosersMatch. <span>The Revenue Ecosystem.</span></p>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  /* ====================================================
     HERO
  ==================================================== */
  .vb-hero {
    background: #fff;
    padding: 162px 0 80px;
  }

  .vb-hero__inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.15fr 1fr;
    gap: 64px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .vb-hero__content .label--red {
    background: rgba(221,52,46,0.1);
    color: var(--color-red);
    border: 1px solid rgba(221,52,46,0.25);
  }

  .vb-hero__title {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 3.8vw, 3.2rem);
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--color-black);
    line-height: 1.08;
    letter-spacing: -0.025em;
    margin: 20px 0 24px;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
  }

  .vb-hero__title-red { color: var(--color-red); }

  .vb-hero__subtitle {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: #4B5563;
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    max-width: 520px;
  }

  .vb-hero__trust-pills {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .trust-pill {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-black);
    background: var(--color-gray-light);
    border-radius: 999px;
    padding: 5px 14px;
    letter-spacing: 0.01em;
  }

  .vb-hero__actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 14px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    align-items: center;
  }

  /* Stats card rechts */
  .vb-hero__stats-card {
    background: var(--color-black);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: 36px 32px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0;
  }

  .vb-stat {
    padding: 20px 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 4px;
  }

  .vb-stat__num {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: #fff;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .vb-stat__label {
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .vb-stat__company {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-red);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-top: 4px;
  }

  .vb-stat-divider {
    height: 1px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
  }

  @media (max-width: 960px) {
    .vb-hero__inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 48px; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 560px) {
    .vb-hero { padding: 100px 0 60px; }
    .vb-hero__actions { flex-direction: column; align-items: stretch; }
    .vb-hero__actions .btn { width: 100%; justify-content: center; }
  }

  /* ====================================================
     PIJNPUNTEN
  ==================================================== */
  .vb-pijn { background: #F9FAFB; }

  .vb-pijn__header {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin-bottom: 56px;
  }

  .vb-pijn__title {
    margin-top: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .vb-pijn__title-red { color: var(--color-red); }

  .vb-pijn__sub {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--color-gray-mid);
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  .vb-pijn__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 24px;
